\usepackage{amsfonts} 
\usepackage{amssymb} 
\usepackage{amsbsy}
\usepackage{mathrsfs}
\usepackage{upgreek}
\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
\begin{document}$$ se{\left( \phi \right)} \approx {\sqrt {\frac{{\phi {\left( {1 - \phi } \right)}}} {r}} } \approx {\sqrt {\frac{{0.9\raise0.145em\hbox{${\scriptscriptstyle \bullet}$}0.1}} {{1000}}} } \approx 0.01 $$\end{document}. In this paper we will ignore this complication and use \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
