\usepackage{mathrsfs}
\usepackage{upgreek}
\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
\begin{document}$$\widehat{\phi }$$\end{document} and ϕ interchangeably.

The proposed bootstrap procedure performed poorly (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
